{"seq":2,"id":"09e7522c","type":"generate","ts":"2026-05-16T11:48:16.912Z","event":{"type":"generate","id":"09e7522c","action":"impeccable","freeformPrompt":"flytta någon annan stans samma för alla scenarier","count":3,"pageUrl":"/parodontologi/gingivit-parodontit","element":{"tagName":"section","id":null,"classes":["rounded-[22px]","p-7","md:p-8","mb-4"],"textContent":"Röda flaggorKritisk · Snabb bennedbrytningBennedbrytning oproportionerlig mot plackbörda — särskilt ung patient → Misstänk Grad C, systemsjukdom (HIV, leukemi), aggressiv parodontit.Kritisk · AbscessbildningAkut parodontal abscess → dränage omedelbart. Se scenario Parodontal Abscess.Varning · SystemsjukdomOkontrollerad diabetes (HbA1c >10%), immunosuppression, neutropeni → Koordinera med läkare. Antibiotika kan vara indicerat.Varning · Tandrörlighet grad 3Tand rörlig i vertikalled eller spontant","outerHTML":"<section class=\"rounded-[22px] p-7 md:p-8 mb-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-label=\"Röda flaggor — klinisk varning\" style=\"background:var(--status-danger);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(193,18,31,0.28)\"><h2 class=\"font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-5 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.3 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.7 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.4 0Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Röda flaggor</h2><ul class=\"space-y-4\" role=\"list\"><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Kritisk · <!-- -->Snabb bennedbrytning</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Bennedbrytning oproportionerlig mot plackbörda — särskilt ung patient → Misstänk Grad C, systemsjukdom (HIV, leukemi), aggressiv parodontit.</p></li><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Kritisk · <!-- -->Abscessbildning</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Akut parodontal abscess → dränage omedelbart. Se scenario Parodontal Abscess.</p></li><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Varning · <!-- -->Systemsjukdom</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Okontrollerad diabetes (HbA1c &gt;10%), immunosuppression, neutropeni → Koordinera med läkare. Antibiotika kan vara indicerat.</p></li><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Varning · <!-- -->Tandrörlighet grad 3</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Tand rörlig i vertikalled eller spontant rörlig → Hopeless prognosis. Diskutera extraktion.</p></li></ul></section>","computedStyles":{"font-family":"\"Plus Jakarta Sans\", \"Plus Jakarta Sans Fallback\"","font-size":"18px","font-weight":"400","line-height":"29.7px","color":"rgb(255, 255, 255)","background":"rgb(193, 18, 31) none repeat scroll 0% 0% / auto padding-box border-box","background-color":"rgb(193, 18, 31)","padding":"36px","margin":"0px 0px 18px","display":"block","position":"static","gap":"normal","border-radius":"22px","box-shadow":"rgba(193, 18, 31, 0.28) 0px 8px 24px 0px"},"cssCustomProperties":{"--font-display":"'Newsreader', 'Newsreader Fallback'","--font-body":"'Plus Jakarta Sans', 'Plus Jakarta Sans Fallback'","--font-mono":"'IBM Plex Mono', 'IBM Plex Mono Fallback'","--tw-border-spacing-x":"0","--tw-border-spacing-y":"0","--tw-translate-x":"0","--tw-translate-y":"0","--tw-rotate":"0","--tw-skew-x":"0","--tw-skew-y":"0","--tw-scale-x":"1","--tw-scale-y":"1","--tw-scroll-snap-strictness":"proximity","--tw-ring-offset-width":"0px","--tw-ring-offset-color":"#fff","--tw-ring-color":"rgb(59 130 246 / 0.5)","--tw-ring-offset-shadow":"0 0 #0000","--tw-ring-shadow":"0 0 #0000","--tw-shadow":"0 0 #0000","--tw-shadow-colored":"0 0 #0000","--tw-bg-opacity":"1","--tw-t